00048 void FusionCHPMultiDataAccessorTest::testRead()
00049 {
00050     vector<string> chps;
00051     chps.push_back("../../parsers/data/CHP_MultiData_file");
00052     FusionCHPMultiDataAccessor accessor;
00053     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(accessor.Initialize(chps) == true);
00054 
00055     vector<string> snps;
00056     snps.push_back("gn1");
00057     snps.push_back("gn2");
00058     vector<vector<u_int8_t>> calls;
00059     vector<vector<float>> confs;
00060     accessor.ExtractData(snps, calls, confs);
00061 
00062     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calls.size() == 1);
00063     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(confs.size() == 1);
00064 
00065     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calls[0].size() == 2);
00066     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(confs[0].size() == 2);
00067 
00068     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calls[0][0] == 1);
00069     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(calls[0][1] == 2);
00070 
00071     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(confs[0][0], 11.0, 0.000001f);
00072     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(confs[0][1], 22.0, 0.000001f);
00073 }
